OL,3,CHistoric tramway back on track after
OL,4,Csecuring major funding
OL,6,FAn historic tramway that has been
OL,7,Fclosed for more than a year because of
OL,8,Felectrical issues is set to reopen
OL,9,Fafter securing nearly half a million
OL,10,Fpounds in funding.
OL,12,FThe popular heritage attraction in
OL,13,FHeaton Park, Manchester, has been out
OL,14,Fof service because the electrical
OL,15,Fsubstation that powers the line
OL,16,Frequired a major overhaul to meet
OL,17,Fcurrent safety standards.
