OL,3,CHistoric tramway back on track after
OL,4,Csecuring major funding
OL,6,FA #481,000 investment from Manchester
OL,7,FCity Council will fund essential
OL,8,Frestoration work on the substation,
OL,9,Fwith work due to begin in spring 2026.
OL,11,FThe upgrade is expected to allow tram
OL,12,Fservices to resume in summer 2026,
OL,13,Fcoinciding with the 125th anniversary
OL,14,Fof Manchester's first electric
OL,15,Ftramways in 1901.
OL,17,FThe heritage tramway runs on the only
OL,18,Fremaining section of the original
OL,19,Ftramway line in Heaton Park.
