OL,3,CHistoric tramway back on track after
OL,4,Csecuring major funding
OL,6,FThe council says the investment will
OL,7,Fsecure the safe operation of the
OL,8,Ftramway for many years to come.
OL,10,FCouncillor Lee-Ann Igbon said: "The
OL,11,Fvintage trams hold a special place in
OL,12,Fthe hearts of many people, and I'm
OL,13,Fdelighted that it will be up and
OL,14,Frunning again in time for the 125
OL,15,Fanniversary."
