OL,3,CHistoric tramway back on track after
OL,4,Csecuring major funding
OL,6,FThe project is described as the
OL,7,Fculmination of decades of work by
OL,8,Fvolunteers from the Manchester
OL,9,FTransport Museum Society (MTMS), who
OL,10,Fhave worked alongside Manchester City
OL,11,FCouncil since 1979 to keep the
OL,12,Fattraction running in one of the
OL,13,Fcity's largest and most popular green
OL,14,Fspaces.
OL,16,FGeoff Senior, Chair of the Manchester
OL,17,FTransport Museum Society, said it is
OL,18,F:wonderful news" because the tramway
OL,19,Fis a "vital piece of Manchester's
OL,20,Ftransport heritage".
